1.6
log
@Kill SPINLOCK_SPIN_HOOK, use CPU_BUSY_CYCLE() instead.

ok visa@@, kettenis@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: lock_machdep.c,v 1.5 2017/04/30 16:45:45 mpi Exp $	*/

/*
